My meme

This meme is about how some parents think that taking away a learning tool (a teens phone) will drastically improve my grades almost immediately. Inspired by a friends story :D

library(magick)

url <- "https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/029/959/Screen_Shot_2019-06-05_at_1.26.32_PM.jpg"

#creates blank square
canvas <- image_blank(width = 500, 
                      height = 200, 
                      color = "#000000") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "what parents think will happen \n when they take phone away",
                 color = "#FFFFFF",
                 size = 35,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "center")

stonks <- image_read(url) %>%
  image_scale(500) %>%
  image_annotate(text = "grades",
                 color = "#000000",
                 size = 85,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "southeast")

joined <- c(canvas, stonks)

appended <- image_append(joined, stack=TRUE)

image_write(appended, "grades_meme.png")

My animated GIF

What can I say? I love cats

library(magick)

canvas <- image_blank(width = 400, 
                      height = 100, 
                      color = "#000000") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "now, cats",
                 color = "#FFFFFF",
                 size = 35,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "center")

cat1 <- image_read("https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FgGY0Q2XkAAwQTe?format=jpg&name=4096x4096") %>%
  image_scale(400) %>%
  image_extent("400x300")

cat1joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat1), stack = TRUE)

cat2 <- image_read("https://www.idlememe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/beluga-cat-meme-idlememe-5.jpg") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat2joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat2), stack = TRUE)

cat3 <- image_read("https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/041/742/cover3.jpg") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat3joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat3), stack = TRUE)

cat4 <- image_read("https://i.cbc.ca/1.5359228.1577206958!/fileImage/httpImage/image.jpg_gen/derivatives/16x9_940/smudge-the-viral-cat.jpg") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat4joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat4), stack = TRUE)

cat5 <- image_read("https://i.redd.it/i-keep-seeing-this-angry-cat-meme-does-anyone-know-what-v0-98vznktg9jw91.jpg?width=1080&format=pjpg&auto=webp&s=ba9c6d8b43fd5b943e6f65688688b2c926f7a6f9") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat5joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat5), stack = TRUE)

cat6 <- image_read("https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAmr-PAWsAEoiWR.jpg") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat6joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat6), stack = TRUE)

cat7 <- image_read("https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/026/489/crying.jpg") %>%
  image_scale(400)

cat7joined <- image_append(c(canvas, cat7), stack = TRUE)

frames <- c(cat1joined,cat2joined,cat3joined,cat4joined,cat5joined,cat6joined,cat7joined)

animation <- image_animate(frames, fps = 5)

image_write(animation, "now_cats.gif")
